"DECREASE ATTRIBUTE"

Category: ^gHEALTH^n
Duration: ^gSUSTAINED^n

The decrease spell affects its targetted attribute and has a TN of 10 
minus the essence of the target. For every two successes the targets 
attribute is decreased by one, up to a maximum of the spells force. 

It only affects non-ware modified attributes.

^WSee Also: CAST, INCREASE ATTRIBUTE, INCREASE CYBERED ATTRIBUTE, DECREASE CYBERED ATTRIBUTE^n

